text: USS Wachusett has been the name of more than one United States Navy ship, and may refer to: *USS Wachusett (1861), a sloop-of-war in commission from 1862 to 1868, from 1871 to 1874, and from 1879 to 1885 *USS Wachusett (ID-1840), a cargo ship in commission from 1918 to 1919 ==See also== *, an armed motorboat in service from 1917 to 1919 Category:United States Navy ship names
title: USS Wachusett
